== Overview ==
The big brother to [[Argon Laser|Argon]], the Baron ultra-light laser can cause significant all round damage to targets.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Baron Laser can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
